message.body:
This is a message from Biggie's mom, ##############
No problem at all. Feel free to give him my cell, etc. also wifi password is ########## if he wants it :)
Please ask him to send her a text that all is well between Friday and Sat
Let me know what time you want to meet there
I can meet u at 6 if that's ok for you
Ok great
I'm at Daniels eating and may be a little late meeting you
Ok, when can you get there?
I'll be 10 or 15 mins late at the most
Ok, I have plans with my friend Emily after. I'll probably just have her meet me there. See you soon and hi to D.
You can drop them here if it's easier for you
Sorry, dinner took longer than we thought
No problem. I wanted to introduce you to Biggie. The feeding, etc. Is 6:15 OK for you?
Ok, see you there
Yes
Me too
On my way now
Hey Sabrina, do u know the email I need to enter to sign in to the wifi? I tried the one she left in the ema and it doesn't work?
Just texted her. I'll let you know if I hear back.
The wifi name is ######and password is ##########
Ok thanks!
No problem. How's the Bigman?
Real good
Excellent! Give him a squeezing for me. Oh yeah, Michelle should be able to pay you next week. She's away this weekend.
Ok no problem
